node.text:
Crafted by the Maison’s workshop in the heart of Paris, the Torsade de Chaumet High Jewellery collection combines creativity and bicentenary excellence to give rise to timeless and undeniably contemporary masterpieces.

Take a tour of the Maison’s High Jewellery workshop and dive into 240 years of mastery.

#Chaumet #TorsadedeChaumet #ChaumetHighJewellery

node.text:
Face of the latest issue of the Maison’s Rendez-Vous magazine, German actress #DianeKruger joins the Chaumet family as new friend of the Maison.

Wearing the Maison’s High Jewellery creations, she recounts in an exclusive interview her first meeting with Chaumet, her intimate relationship with jewels as well as the singularity of Chaumet’s High Jewellery creations.

#Chaumet #ChaumetRendezVous #ChaumetHighJewellery

#Chaumet #ChaumetSummer #SummerinParis #ChaumetWatches

#Chaumet #TorsadedeChaumet #ChaumetHighJewellery
